overview: Combo Holidays Ltd was established since 2011 and was trading under name of First Choice Hotels Ltd till 2012, keeping this is mind. We are a renowned travel company based in Europe, United States, Mexico and Middle East with a reach that spans across the globe. Not only the best accommodation, we offer an extensive database of holiday packages, car hire, cruise trips, sightseeing tours. With us, you can book your preference from more than 180 airlines and over 85,000 hotels all around the world.
